==English==
===Pronunciation===
[[IPA]]: /heɪl/

===Etymology===
From Old English [[hægl|hæġl]].

====Noun====
'''hail''' (''uncountable'')

#Balls of [[ice]] falling as [[precipitation]] from the sky.

